title: The Chilling Adventures of Sabrina Episode 1 "October Country" Breakdown!
author: Think Story
comment: What do you guys think? Should I do each episode or one for the entire season?
You’re the only one breaking down CAOS, pls don’t stop 🖤
Yes danny! just started this today. Do a break down of each episode (milk it like a shane dawson documentary)

I am loving the individual breakdowns. The darker side of Sabrina the Teenage Witch is definitely interesting. Even if I can't watch it, the breakdowns are helping understand it and so far, I am liking this version of Salem. Instead of a warlock cursed for doing something 'stupid', he's a darker spirit of a Salem warlock killed in the trials. Definitely liking this so far.

Dr Sapirstein is a nod to Rosemary’s baby just FYI. 
Wardwell tells the “girl” she picked up on the road at night that she’ll take her home and call Dr Sapirstein in the morning. 
Loved that!!
